        {
          "type": "reasoning",
          "text": "The user wants to add resource limits to the docker-compose.yml file. I can see the current file has a single `db` service (PostgreSQL). I need to plan adding resource limits (memory and CPU) to this service.\n\nSince I'm in plan mode, I should present a plan for adding resource limits rather than making the edit.",
