          "messageID": "msg_e6415f263002eevuqMWJlDIv3e"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Add `deploy.resources.limits` to the `db` service in `docker-compose.yml`:\n\n```yaml\ndeploy:\n  resources:\n    limits:\n      cpus: \"1\"\n      memory: 512M\n    reservations:\n      cpus: \"0.5\"\n      memory: 256M\n```\n\nThis sets:\n- **Limits**: max 1 CPU core, 512MB RAM\n- **Reservations**: guaranteed 0.5 CPU, 256MB RAM\n\nReasonable for a dev Postgres instance. Want different values, or should I proceed with these?",
          "time": {
            "start": 1779795624193,
            "end": 1779795625281
          },
